{"type": "article", "id": 34059, "title": "上海中心拿下美国建筑最高奖，以及，日牌 ato 的春夏系列值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-03T03:11:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 30, "name": "Paul Smith"}, {"id": 16574, "name": "Evisu"}, {"id": 16796, "name": "Zippo"}, {"id": 22487, "name": "上海中心"}, {"id": 34585, "name": "美国建筑奖"}, {"id": 34586, "name": "ato"}, {"id": 34587, "name": "打火机"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 34588, "name": "Amzon"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161103102317ibuSsJO84rePa2kE.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/11/02/shanghai-tower-skyscraper-gensler-wins-first-american-architecture-prize/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>上海中心拿下了今年美国建筑奖的最高奖项</b></a> | 上海中心由总部位于旧金山的建筑设计公司 Gensler 设计，它拿下了<a href=\"https://architectureprize.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2016 American Architecture Prize </a>最高奖项。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/lauder-sales-inch-up-with-makeup-segment-hampered-by-mac-10695586/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>M.A.C 增速放缓，抑制其母公司业绩增长 </b></a>| 在第一个财政季度，由于 M.A.C 增速放缓，抑制其母公司雅诗兰黛集团的增长。雅诗兰黛集团的净收入下降至 2.94 亿美元，净销售额仅增长了 1%，至 28.7 亿美元。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-11-02/amazon-said-to-consider-bid-for-stake-in-dubai-s-souq-com\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Amazon 或将投资迪拜电商网站</b></a> | 据 bloomberg 消息，作为在中东市场的扩张计划之一，Amazon 在考虑投资迪拜电商网站 Souq.com FZ，该电商公司的最少估值为 12 亿美元，而 Amazon 的这笔交易或将占有 Souq 的 30% 股份。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/forecasts-analysis/edited-activewear-10697380/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>运动休闲类的服装中，Nike 的市场表现最好</b></a> | 实时数据分析机构 Edited 发布了一份报告，该报告调研了两年内超过 1700 个服装品牌及 40000 个单品，指出市场表现最好的仍然是 Nike，它在过去一年实现了 82% 的增长，Under Armour 紧随其后，Adidas 位列第三。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>推荐日本品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/ato-ss17\" rel=\"nofollow\">ato 的 2017 春夏系列</a>。 ato 由设计师松本与在 1993 年创立，品牌强调版型的概念，每件单品都是立体裁剪，ato 还给每件衣服都加上了版型师的名字。在新的 2017 系列中，主打黑、灰、卡其等色调，采用宽松加长的剪裁手法，抢眼却不浮夸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094523MNOpzlwyYeZQGKb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094524xOzqbhoFiUdkDwpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611030945230TEIB34frFGSt96N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094524MTUo1wyELmI4j6Xi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094524LlQSGU1pFcNKv3ge.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094524a7rkWlRzP3fgZ2sU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094524bd4tNqAjsz8TFWiP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094524cwGgaJHERM4iDPqu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094537Sey0cBwCvNAg8EtP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094537dOefqWEx54riv9DZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611030945370wtnFz4c7gWDqG61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>英伦经典 Paul Smith 再度与英国经典品牌 Anglepoise® 合作，带来 Edition Three 新版经典 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/paul-smith-x-anglepoise-type-75-desk-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Type 75™ </a>台灯。这款台灯采用了明亮的白色以及红色、黄色及蓝色作三原色，色彩对比强烈，现已登陆 Paul Smith 各大门店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094548mSve7AqiUnj9h23G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">秋冬保暖，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/stussy-gore-tex-parka-2016-fw\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stussy 与 GORE-TEX 的合作款大衣</a>还不错。这款大衣采用了防水材质，并有橄榄绿和黑色的双色选择，呈现出军事与运动的叠加风格。将于 11 月 4 日正式登陆 Stussy 门店，售价约为 560 美元。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103101435A2LvxbR3sCapZV9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/evisu-x-zippo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Evisu 与美国打火机品牌 Zippo 合作</a>，推出限量版打火机。在经典的打火机上加入了 Evisu 的经典标志，还有模仿牛仔裤针线的细节。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094601uNzZWjmGM1V7QUpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094612kgja2CB7IA0x5dey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094612JBaSVLYcje8dikEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110309461262quoG80DOgEjHaS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">香奈儿发布 2016／17 早春度假系列，卡尔·拉格斐再度亲自掌镜，并请来苏格兰超模 Stella Tennant 和阿根廷超模 Mica Arganaraz 出境演绎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094626TeFknB8jVf2ozKHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094636V0UtxBWjmM2yHodY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094637d4BXbLKwrIy5tOWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094638LxpOVkSfgTNui0KH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094646JUnva3pOByQIHqA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094654Y3k1LtTnNOKA2QbJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161103094654OvIFs8gieA90bG71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}